it/tag/giovanna-lanza/" rel="tag">Giovanna Lanza</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/giovanni-battista-rigon/" rel="tag">giovanni battista rigon</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/la-gazza-ladra/" rel="tag">La gazza ladra</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/majella-cullagh/" rel="tag">majella cullagh</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/mario-zeffiri/" rel="tag">Mario Zeffiri</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/mirco-palazzi/" rel="tag">Mirco Palazzi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/omar-montanari/" rel="tag">omar montanari</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/paolo-fantin/" rel="tag">Paolo Fantin</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/roberto-tagliavini/" rel="tag">Roberto Tagliavini</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/silvia-regazzo/" rel="tag">silvia regazzo</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Carla Teti, Gioachino Rossini, Giovanna Lanza, giovanni battista rigon, La gazza ladra, majella cullagh, Mario Zeffiri, Mirco Palazzi, omar montanari, Opera lirica, Paolo Fantin, Roberto Tagliavini, silvia regazzo"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/d2cbd2955f184be4e4dc5cf0b8285a11" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/mia-foto-e1385566919652.jpg" width="1" height="1" alt="Giorgio Bagnoli" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Giorgio Bagnoli"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></